data.description: This Gorgeous, 5 Bedroom, 3 Bath Charmer With A 3 Car Garage Is A MUST SEE!! Enter Into The Spacious Family Room Which Offers; Vaulted Ceilings & Tons Of Natural Light. Continue Through The Formal Dining Area To The Kitchen Which Boasts; All Black Appliances, Granite Counters & Tons Of Cabinet Space. Dining Area & The Living Room Off Of The Kitchen Offers A Gas Fireplace Making This A Perfect Space For Family Gatherings. The Upstairs Primary Bedroom Offers; Tons Of Space w/Its Own Sitting Area, An En Suite Bath w/Double Sinks & A Walk in Closet. Ceiling Fans Throughout! The Spacious Backyard Offers Tons Of Entertainment Potential, Perfect For Those Summer BBQs w/Friends & Family! Conveniently Located To The Airport, The Strip, Shopping and Several Parks Including Sunset Park. Minutes From Both I 215 & I 15 Making Getting Around The Valley Quick & Easy! Water Heater Less Than 1 Year Old, AC Unit & High End Solar.
